[
  {"speaker":"char_lu_wu_shuang","speaker_name":"陆无双","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"这怪人在这儿坐了老半天啦，怎么动也不动？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"何沅君呢？何沅君到那里去了？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"是啊，十年啦，十年来都没人陪我玩。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"你不是阿沅？不是我的阿沅？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_lu_wu_shuang","listener_name":"陆无双","text":"陆展元这小畜生死了？几时死的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"死了，死了！","tone":"悲伤","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_lu_wu_shuang","listener_name":"陆无双","text":"死得好，死得好，只可惜我不能亲手取他狗命。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_hong_ling_bo","speaker_name":"洪凌波","listener":"char_lu_li_ding","listener_name":"陆立鼎","text":"但取陆家一门七口性命，余人快快出去。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_lu_li_ding","speaker_name":"陆立鼎","listener":"char_lu_er_niang","listener_name":"陆二娘","text":"娘子，陆家满门今日倘若难逃一死，也让咱们死得不堕了兄嫂的威名。","tone":"激动","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_li_mo_chou","speaker_name":"李莫愁","listener":"char_lu_li_ding","listener_name":"陆立鼎","text":"陆二爷，你哥哥倘若尚在，只要他出口求我，再休了何沅君那小贱人，我未始不可饶了你家一门良贱。如今，唉，你们运气不好，只怪你哥哥太短命，可怪不得我。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_li_mo_chou","speaker_name":"李莫愁","listener":"char_wu_san_tong","listener_name":"武三通","text":"问世间，情是何物，直教生死相许？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":1,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_wu_san_tong","speaker_name":"武三通","listener":"char_li_mo_chou","listener_name":"李莫愁","text":"李姑娘，十年不见，你好啊。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_li_mo_chou","speaker_name":"李莫愁","listener":"char_wu_san_tong","listener_name":"武三通","text":"我曾立过重誓，谁在我面前提起这贱人的名字，不是他死，就是我亡。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_li_mo_chou","speaker_name":"李莫愁","listener":"char_cheng_ying","listener_name":"程英","text":"你这等模样，他日长大了，若非让别人伤心，便是自己伤心，不如及早死了，世界上少了好些烦恼。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_li_mo_chou","listener_name":"李莫愁","text":"喂，你们到我家里来干么？","tone":"调侃","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_li_mo_chou","listener_name":"李莫愁","text":"啧啧，大美人儿好美貌，小美人儿也挺秀气，两位姑娘是来找我的吗？姓杨的可没这般美人儿朋友啊。","tone":"调侃","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_guo_jing","speaker_name":"郭靖","listener":"char_huang_rong","listener_name":"黄蓉","text":"你说是像……","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_huang_rong","speaker_name":"黄蓉","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"你姓杨名过，你妈妈姓穆，是不是？","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_guo_jing","listener_name":"郭靖","text":"我妈妈死啦，死了很久啦！","tone":"悲伤","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_ou_yang_feng","listener_name":"欧阳锋","text":"爸爸，爸爸！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":2,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_huang_rong","speaker_name":"黄蓉","listener":"char_guo_jing","listener_name":"郭靖","text":"我就怕他聪明过份了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_guo_jing","speaker_name":"郭靖","listener":"char_huang_rong","listener_name":"黄蓉","text":"他父虽行止不端，但郭杨两家世代交好，我瞧他相貌清秀，聪明伶俐，今后跟着咱俩，将来不愁不能出人头地。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_huang_rong","speaker_name":"黄蓉","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"子曰：学而时习之，不亦说乎？有朋自远方来，不亦乐乎？","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_guo_jing","listener_name":"郭靖","text":"我爹爹是你跟郭伯母害死的，是不是？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_guo_jing","speaker_name":"郭靖","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"过几天我送你去终南山重阳宫，求全真教长春子丘真人收你入门。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_wu_xiu_wen","listener_name":"武修文","text":"是啊，疯狗见人就咬，人家好端端的在这里，三条疯狗却过来乱吠乱叫。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_guo_jing","listener_name":"郭靖","text":"郭伯伯，我不跟臭道士学武功，我要跟你学。","tone":"恳求","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_qiu_qian_ren","listener_name":"丘处机","text":"他不是奸贼！他是好人。你打死我好了，我一句话也不说。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":3,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_guo_jing","speaker_name":"郭靖","listener":"char_ma_yu","listener_name":"马钰","text":"大胆贼子，竟敢到重阳宫来撒野！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_guo_jing","listener_name":"郭靖","text":"郭伯伯，我在这里。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_qiu_qian_ren","listener_name":"丘处机","text":"师祖爷教训得是，弟子今后要力求上进，才不负了师祖爷的期望。","tone":"陈述","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_zhao_zhi_jing","listener_name":"赵志敬","text":"臭道士，贼头狗脑的山羊胡子牛鼻子，既不教我半点武功，又这般打我，怎么还配做我师父？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_zhao_zhi_jing","speaker_name":"赵志敬","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"畜生，你当真不想活了？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_zhao_zhi_jing","listener_name":"赵志敬","text":"你以后还打我不打？","tone":"疑问","chapter":4,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_xiao_long_nyu","listener_name":"小龙女","text":"杨过今日拜小龙女姑姑为师，自今而后，杨过永远听姑姑的话，要一生一世照料姑姑周全。倘若姑姑有甚危难凶险，杨过要舍了自己性命保护姑姑，如有坏人来欺侮姑姑，杨过拚了命也要将他杀了。","tone":"激动","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_sun_po_po","speaker_name":"孙婆婆","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"好孩子，你师父是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_sun_po_po","speaker_name":"孙婆婆","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"孩子，别人不要你，婆婆偏喜欢你。你跟我走，不管去那里，婆婆总跟你一起。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_sun_po_po","speaker_name":"孙婆婆","listener":"char_xiao_long_nyu","listener_name":"小龙女","text":"我求你照料他一生一世，别让他吃旁人半点亏，你答不答允？","tone":"恳求","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_sun_po_po","speaker_name":"孙婆婆","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"你龙姑姑无依无靠，你……你……也……照料她……一生一世……","tone":"恳求","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"人人都要死，那也算不了什么。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"欺侮幼儿老妇，算得什么英雄好汉？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_hao_da_tong","listener_name":"郝大通","text":"怎么？你不自刎相谢，竟要我动手么？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"我死之前，自然先杀了你。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"我答允孙婆婆要照料你一生一世。我不离开这儿，你自然也在这儿。","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_xiao_long_nyu","speaker_name":"小龙女","listener":"char_yang_guo","listener_name":"杨过","text":"天下男子就没个好人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_xiao_long_nyu","listener_name":"小龙女","text":"我心里当你师父，敬你重你，你说什么我就做什么，可是我口里不叫你师父，只叫你姑姑。","tone":"恳求","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0},
  {"speaker":"char_yang_guo","speaker_name":"杨过","listener":"char_xiao_long_nyu","listener_name":"小龙女","text":"谁待我不好，他就是打我，我也不肯输一句口。谁待我好呢，我为他死了也心甘情愿，何况讨一句饶？","tone":"激动","chapter":5,"line_start":0,"line_end":0}
]